      "span_text": "Additionally, because no full-scale studies regarding the behavior of RAC structures have been made, the evaluation of possible size effects is a necessary step toward the use of RAC (for instance, the ductility of a scaled-down specimen can overestimate the actual ductility of a structure, as argued by [CITATION_1] )."
